ing-jeou-rejects-japans-claims-diaoyu-islands-during-mainland-china-trip?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国游客斥巨资庆祝2019年以来最赚钱的清明节</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3258138/chinese-travellers-spend-big-mark-most-profitable-ching-ming-festival-2019?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>周六结束的三天假期，国内出行量超过 1.19 亿人次，收入接近 540 亿元人民币，远高于大流行前的水平。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 10:59:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3258138/chinese-travellers-spend-big-mark-most-profitable-ching-ming-festival-2019?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>解决中美关系必须以老百姓的生活为中心</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/opinion/china-opinion/article/3258113/fix-us-china-relations-we-must-centre-lives-ordinary-people?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>到中国旅行让美国学生体会到了这个国家的复杂性，并与中国人民分享了欢乐的时刻。美国人和中国人之间的面对面互动必须保留，即使是在两国政府之间的关系变得更加紧张的情况下。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 09:30:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/opinion/china-opinion/article/3258113/fix-us-china-relations-we-must-centre-lives-ordinary-people?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国华为凭借突破性的人工智能模型“知己”再次挑战传统天气预报</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3257969/chinas-huawei-challenging-traditional-weather-forecasting-again-time-groundbreaking-ai-model-zhiji?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>基于华为盘古天气的突破性人工智能模型知己可以提供五天的预报，精度仅为3公里。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 09:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3257969/chinas-huawei-challenging-traditional-weather-forecasting-again-time-groundbreaking-ai-model-zhiji?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国、英国、澳大利亚“准备就扩大奥库斯安全协议进行谈判”以威慑中国，日本可能是候选者</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3258126/us-uk-australia-set-talks-expanding-aukus-security-pact-deter-china-japan-likely-candidate?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>据《金融时报》援引知情人士的话报道，会谈将涉及该