.scmp.com/opinion/china-opinion/article/3257839/ching-ming-lets-sweep-away-fusty-chinese-ideas-death-and-dying?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>不愿谈论死亡可能会让我们无法与所爱的人好好告别。但随着现代教育和年轻人登记遗嘱，人们的态度正在发生变化。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 01:30:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/opinion/china-opinion/article/3257839/ching-ming-lets-sweep-away-fusty-chinese-ideas-death-and-dying?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item></channel></rss>